text: Marta Colaiocco (born 24 February 1984) is an Italian water polo player and coach. She was a member of the Italian women's national water polo team. She played at the 2011 FINA Women's Water Polo World League. She coached for Firenze Waterpolo. == References == Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:Italian water polo players Category:Italian water polo coaches
